{
  "texts": [
    "In silico methods have recently become very popular for the prediction of DDIs.",
    "They provide a cost-effective and efficient screening tool for DDIs.",
    "However, representing molecules is a challenging task.",
    "Different molecular representations have been proposed, such as chemical descriptors and fingerprints [1].",
    "Chemical descriptors are quantitative measurements of a molecule's structural, physical, or chemical properties."
  ]
}